{"tid":874794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國遊客不觀光　結夥專挑寺廟偷香油錢","createTime":"2018-10-24T12:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T14:25:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ffcc8a6e7bc6f0c4f9eab6c5d1e1b4a6a1d92677","tid":874794,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181024/640_a6f49e0b0c477a32def47d7b5b20147f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181024%2F640_a6f49e0b0c477a32def47d7b5b20147f.jpg&h=560e46db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國遊客到泰國的寺廟偷香油錢，被人贓俱獲，警方還說根據他們的手法，應該是慣竊。<br />\n<br />\n據泰國《khaosod》報導，10月22日，泰國警方接到巴威區一處寺廟的報警電話，稱廟內的香油錢明顯變少，認為是有人偷走，於是警方抵達現場後，觀看監視器畫面，立刻發現有兩名可疑男子出現，其中一人在香油錢箱前，用道具釣出箱子裡面的金錢，而另一個人在附近把風。<br />\n<br />\n當這領名中國遊客離開現場後，警方立即出動將他們逮捕，並從他們身上起出、890泰銖(約840新台幣)、膠帶、繩子等做案工具。這兩名37歲、39歲中國遊客指出，是從上海到泰國，聽朋友說該寺廟很漂亮才前來。警方表示，從兩人的手法跟工具來看，應該是在泰國各寺廟行竊的慣犯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181024/1453678/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181024%2F1453678%2F&d=TfZYDYXcrxxb4%2B8FkDEgtsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=56c54037\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181024%2F1453678%2F&h=887030c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181024/1453678/</a>"},{"pid":"fb563d7c7a3a98f466528f7466b24886447df42e","tid":874794,"uid":9338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c147d97173acf25164fdf4f9a87ff78b0129bc3","tid":874794,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:25:32.000Z","msg":"無可能 隔離po話香港人最衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}